s et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Sed euismod magna a nibh.\r\n\r\nSed euismod magna a nibh. Praesent rutrum sapien ac felis. Phasellus elementum dolor quis turpis. Vestibulum nec mi vitae pede tincidunt nonummy. Praesent rutrum sapien ac felis. Phasellus elementum dolor quis turpis. Vestibulum nec mi vitae pede tincidunt nonummy. Vestibulum facilisis mollis neque.\r\n<p class=\"nomarginbottom\">Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus.Praesent rutrum sapien ac felis. Phasellus elementum dolor quis turpis. Vestibulum nec mi vitae pede tincidunt nonummy. Vestibulum facilisis mollis neque. Sed orci. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\nHere some examples are images with dynamic shadow.<strong> The shadow is automatically added this with only one class added to the image.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Just like this &lt;img src=\"images/image.jpg\" class=\"shadow1\" alt=\"image\" /&gt;\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"shadow1\" src=\"images/shadow-test.jpg\" alt=\"shadow-test\" width=\"547\" height=\"259\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>&lt;img src=\"images/image.jpg\" class=\"shadow2\" alt=\"image\" /&gt;</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"shadow2\" src=\"images/shadow-test.jpg\" alt=\"shadow-test\" width=\"547\" height=\"259\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>&lt;img src=\"images/image.jpg\" class=\"shadow3\" alt=\"image\" /&gt;</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"shadow3\" src=\"images/shadow-test.jpg\" alt=\"shadow-test\" width=\"547\" height=\"259\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>&lt;img src=\"images/image.jpg\" class=\"shadow4\" alt=\"image\" /&gt;</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"shadow4\" src=\"images/shadow-test.jpg\" alt=\"shadow-test\" width=\"547\" height=\"259\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>&lt;img src=\"images/image.jpg\" class=\"shadow5\" alt=\"image\" /&gt;</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"shadow5\" src=\"images/shadow-test.jpg\" alt=\"shadow-test\" width=\"547\" height=\"259\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>&lt;img src=\"images/image.jpg\" class=\"shadow6\" alt=\"image\" /&gt;</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"shadow6\" src=\"images/shadow-test.jpg\" alt=\"shadow-test\" width=\"547\" height=\"259\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>&lt;img src=\"images/image.jpg\" class=\"shadow7\" alt=\"image\" /&gt;</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"shadow7\" src=\"images/shadow-test.jpg\" alt=\"shadow-test\" width=\"547\" height=\"259\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>&lt;img src=\"images/image.jpg\" class=\"shadow8\" alt=\"image\" /&gt;</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"shadow8\" src=\"images/shadow-test.jpg\" alt=\"shadow-test\" width=\"547\" height=\"259\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>&lt;img src=\"images/image.jpg\" class=\"shadow9\" alt=\"image\" /&gt;</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"shadow9\" src=\"images/shadow-test.jpg\" alt=\"shadow-test\" width=\"547\" height=\"259\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>&lt;img src=\"images/image.jpg\" class=\"shadow10\" alt=\"image\" /&gt;</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"shadow10\" src=\"images/shadow-test.jpg\" alt=\"shadow-test\" width=\"547\" height=\"259\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThere are <strong>11 stylistic module class suffixes</strong>, these add a unique style variation to the module: <strong>box1-7</strong> and <strong>title1-4</strong>; and 26 structural suffixes, these affect the layout and metrics of the module.\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>", "Template Typography", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "801-revision-4", "", "", "2012-08-12 02:43:43", "2012-08-11 20:43:43", "", "801", "http://107.22.236.217/lux-spa/?p=808", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `bdt_posts` VALUES("809", "1", "2012-08-12 02:51:50", "2012-08-11 20:51:50", "<h3>Creating Beautiful Content With Simple Code</h3>\r\nTypography is a fundamental part of a template, providing you with the tools to characterise your content and bring it to life. There is a vast array of typography available with Natural Beauty template, as is with our previous releases, from list styles, notice blocks and a diverse number of other elements.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"grid-6 alpha\">\r\n<div class=\"module-title\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\">&lt;h1&gt; Heading Styles</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1>H1. Heading 1</h1>\r\n<h2>H2. Heading 2</h2>\r\n<h3>H3. Heading 3</h3>\r\n<h4>H4. Heading 4</h4>\r\n<h5>H5. Heading 5</h5>\r\n<h1 class=\"rt-pagetitle\">H1. Component Page Title</h1>\r\n<h1 class=\"title nomarginbottom\">H1. Component Content Title</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"grid-6 omega\">\r\n<div class=\"module-title\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\">&lt;ul&gt; List Styles</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>This is an example of a standard list style.</em> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec sit amet nibh.</li>\r\n	<li><em>This is an example of a standard list style.</em> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec sit amet nibh.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"dots\">\r\n	<li>To use this style create a list in the following format: <strong>&lt;ul class=\"</strong><em class=\"normal\">dots</em><strong>\"&gt;&lt;li&gt;....&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;....&lt;/li&gt;...&lt;/ul&gt; (HTML)</strong>.</li>\r\n	<li>To use this style create a list in the following format: <strong>[list class=\" dots\"][li]....[/li][li....[/li][/list] (SHORTCODE)</strong>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"title5 largepaddingbottom\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"grid-6 alpha\">\r\n<div class=\"module-title\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\">&lt;p&gt; DropCap Styles</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"dropcap\">Praesent rutrum sapien ac felis. Phasellus elementum dolor quis turpis. Vestibulum nec mi vitae pede tincidunt nonummy. Vestibulum facilisis mollis neque. Sed orci. Cum sociis natoque penatibu. Pellentesque vel enim urna, sit amet blandit ipsum. Maecenas quis sem sit amet nunc pretium mattis. Sed dapibus semper est, sed pretium erat.</p>\r\nUse the following format: <strong>&lt;p class=\"dropcap\"&gt;...&lt;/p&gt; (HTML)</strong> or <strong>[dropcap class=\"dropcap\"]...[/dropcap] (SHORTCODE)</strong>. You can use any letter, symbol or number.\r\n<p class=\"dropcap2\">Praesent rutrum sapien ac felis. Use this format: <strong>&lt;p class=\"dropcap2\"&gt;...&lt;/p&gt; (HTML)</strong> or <strong>[dropcap class=\"dropcap2\"] ... [/dropcap] (SHORTCODE)</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"dropcap3\">Praesent rutrum sapien ac felis. Use this format: <strong>&lt;p class=\"dropcap3\"&gt;...&lt;/p&gt; (HTML)</strong> or <strong>[dropcap class=\"dropcap3\"] ... [/dropcap] (SHORTCODE)</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"dropcap4\">Praesent rutrum sapien ac felis. Use this format: <strong>&lt;p class=\"dropcap4\"&gt;...&lt;/p&gt; (HTML)</strong> or <strong>[dropcap class=\"dropcap4\"] ... [/dropcap] (SHORTCODE)</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"dropcap5 nomarginbottom\">Praesent rutrum sapien ac felis. Use this format: <strong>&lt;p class=\"dropcap5\"&gt;...&lt;/p&gt; (HTML)</strong> or <strong>[dropcap class=\"dropcap5\"] ... [/dropcap] (SHORTCODE)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"grid-6 omega\">\r\n<div class=\"module-title\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\">&lt;blockquote&gt; Styles</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<blockquote>To replicate, use the following formatting: <strong>&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;....&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt; (HTML)</strong> or <strong>[blockquote class=\"default\"]...[/blockquote] (SHORTCODE)</strong>.</blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote class=\"alignleft\">Praesent rutrum sapien ac felis. Phasellus elementum dolor quis turpis.</blockquote>\r\nTo replicate, use the following formatting: <strong>&lt;blockquote class=\"alignleft\"&gt;&lt;p&gt;....&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt; (HTML)</strong> or <strong>[blockquote class=\"alignleft\"]...[/blockquote] (SHORTCODE)</strong>.\r\n\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Mauris metus tortor.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote class=\"alignright nomarginbottom\">Praesent rutrum sapien ac felis. Phasellus elementum dolor quis turpis.</blockquote>\r\nTo replicate, use the following formatting: <strong>&lt;blockquote class=\"alignright\"&gt;&lt;p&gt;....&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt; (HTML)</strong> or <strong>[blockquote class=\"alignright\"]...[/blockquote] (SHORTCODE)</strong>.\r\n<p class=\"nomarginbottom\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Mauris metus tortor.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"title5 largepaddingbottom\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"grid-6 alpha\">\r\n<div class=\"module-title\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\">&lt;pre&gt; Code Styles</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<pre class=\"lines\">This is a sample <strong>&lt;pre class=\"lines\"&gt;...&lt;/pre&gt; (HTML)</strong> or,\r\n<strong>[pre2 class=\"{lines}\"] ... [/pre2] (SHORTCODE)</strong> tag:\r\ndiv.modulebox-black div.bx1 {\r\n  background: url(../images/box_bl.png) 0 100% repeat;\r\n}\r\ndiv.modulebox-black div.bx2 {\r\n  background: url(../images/box_tr.png) 100% 0 repeat;\r\n}</pre>\r\n<pre class=\"nomarginbottom\">This is a sample <strong>&lt;pre&gt;...&lt;/pre&gt; (HTML)</strong> or, \r\n<strong>[pre class=\"{lines}\"] ... [/pre] (SHORTCODE)</strong> tag:\r\ndiv.modulebox-black div.bx1 {\r\n  background: url(../images/box_bl.png) 0 100% repeat;\r\n}\r\ndiv.modulebox-black div.bx2 {\r\n  background: url(../images/box_tr.png) 100% 0 repeat;\r\n}</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"grid-6 omega\">\r\n<div class=\"module-title\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\">&lt;p&gt; Notice Styles</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"approved\">This is a <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\">sample</a> of the <em>Approved</em> style. To replicate, use the following syntax: <em>&lt;p class=\"approved\"&gt;....&lt;/p&gt;</em> (HTML) or <em>[notice class=\"approved\"] <em class=\"normal\">...</em> [/notice]</em> (SHORTCODE).</p>\r\n<p class=\"attention\">This is a <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\">sample</a> of the <em>Attention</em> style. To replicate, use the following syntax: <em>&lt;p class=\"attention\"&gt;....&lt;/p&gt;</em> (HTML) or <em>[notice class=\"attention\"] <em class=\"normal\">...</em> [/notice]</em> (SHORTCODE).</p>\r\n<p class=\"notice\">This is a <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\">sample</a> of the <em>Notice</em> style. To replicate, use the following syntax: <em>&lt;p class=\"notice\"&gt;....&lt;/p&gt;</em> (HTML) or <em>[notice class=\"notice\"] <em class=\"normal\">...</em> [/notice]</em> (SHORTCODE).</p>\r\n<p class=\"alert nomarginbottom\">This is a <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\">sample</a> of the <em>Alert</em> style. To replicate, use the following syntax: <em>&lt;p class=\"alert\"&gt;....&lt;/p&gt;</em> (HTML) or <em>[notice class=\"alert\"] <em class=\"normal\">...</em> [/notice]</em> (SHORTCODE).</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"title5 largepaddingbottom\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"grid-6 alpha\">\r\n<div class=\"module-title\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\">&lt;span&gt; Text Icon Styles</h3>\r\n</div>\r\nTo replicate, the following format: <strong>&lt;span class=\"text-icon iconname\"&gt;...&lt;/span&gt; (HTML)</strong> or <strong>[icon class=\"icon name\"]...[/icon] (SHORTCODE)</strong>. The class names are listed below, such as \"<strong>text-icon email</strong>\".\r\n<div class=\"grid-6 alpha\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon email\">Text with an email icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon phone\">Text with a phone icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon quote\">Text with a quote icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon cart\">Text with a cart icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon rss\">Text with a rss icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon tags\">Text with a tags icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon write\">Text with a write icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon info\">Text with an info icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon sound\">Text with a sound icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon rightarrow\">Text with a rightarrow icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon leftarrow\">Text with a leftarrow icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon circlearrow\">Text with a circlearrow icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon downarrow\">Text with a downarrow icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon uparrow\">Text with an uparrow icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon person\">Text with a person icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon calendar\">Text with a calendar icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon doc\">Text with a doc icon</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"grid-6 omega\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon bulb\">Text with a bulb icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon twitter\">Text with a twitter icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon youtube\">Text with a youtube icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon skype\">Text with a skype icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon facebook\">Text with a facebook icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon like\">Text with a like icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon video\">Text with a video icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon dropbox\">Text with a dropbox icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon vimeo\">Text with a vimeo icon</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"text-icon paypal\">Text with a paypal icon</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"grid-6 omega\">\r\n<div class=\"module-title\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\">&lt;em&gt; Emphasis Styles</h3>\r\n</div>\r\nThis is a emphasis tag that allows you to <em class=\"italic\">highlight words or phrases</em>. Use the following format: <strong>&lt;em class=\"italic\"&gt;...&lt;/em&gt; (HTML)</strong> or <strong>[emphasis]...[/emphasis] (SHORTCODE)</strong>\r\n\r\nThis is a emphasis tag that all